Class AnterosCupsClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.com.anteros.cups4j.AnterosCupsClient

  • public class AnterosCupsClient
extends Object
    Main Client for accessing CUPS features like

    - get printers

    - print documents

    - get job attributes

    - ...
